data.description: This home is simply gorgeous!  Location is PRIME, located at the top of Thanksgiving mountain.  Private setting, backing up to the beautiful Hill Country with beautiful views of Lake LBJ.  A serene setting inside of the private courtyard with a picture perfect private pool & hot tub!  Some of the  highlights include a double granite island with an onyx backsplash, secluded pool with hot tub and propane heater.  The wet bar includes copper sink and wine fridge, pull out drawers in the kitchen and cabinets.  The master bedroom has a large sitting area, beautiful bathroom with his/her closets, light & bright. THE CASITA offers a separate area for teenagers or in laws and has its own full size bathroom.  This room opens up to the the pool and courtyard area.  This home has 3 outdoor areas all are beautiful as well as very private.  There is a separate work room off of the oversized 2 car garage.  The attic also has floored space and a solar board barrier for more economical electric bills, as well as the 3 HVAC units. The landscaping is perfect, beautiful potted plants surround the courtyard & big trees surround the home!  This home was specifically designed to be centered around the spectacular courtyard area with pool and hot tub.  Each room opens up directly to the courtyard.  There is also a backyard fully fenced with porch and Tv to handle pets or overflow of guests etc.   Thanksgiving Mountain is a highly sought after area with stunning views of Lake LBJ.
